OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPlan to cut energy bills if
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fyou avoid peak-time use    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Households with smart meters could get 
OL,6, discounts on electricity bills if they 
OL,7, use less energy at peak times.         
OL,9,FNational Grid hopes to roll out a      
OL,10,Fscheme where people can save cash if   
OL,11,Fthey avoid high-power activities, such 
OL,12,Fas cooking or charging electric cars,  
OL,13,Fwhen demand is high.                   
OL,15,FThe move follows a trial where Octopus 
OL,16,FEnergy offered incentives for 100,000  
OL,17,Fcustomers who reduced consumption.     
OL,19,FNational Grid is asking all suppliers  
OL,20,Ffor feedback on its plans.             
